<section id="sect_source_mobile6">

<title>MOBILE6 library</title>

<para>The code for the library version of MOBILE6 is in <filename class="directory"><envar>$SMKROOT</envar>/src/mo6</filename>, also accessible with the <envar>M6_SRC</envar> environment variable. This code is the stand-alone version of MOBILE6.2.03 with special aggregation code to create the emission factors at the resolution needed by SMOKE. In addition, we have added code to allow MOBILE6 to pass the emission factors back to SMOKE in memory, rather than writing an output file. The SMOKE version of MOBILE6 has also been updated to allow lowercase input file names and to look for external input files in the <filename class="directory"><envar>$SMK_M6PATH</envar></filename> directory.</para>

</section>

